---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="zh-Hant">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>秘鍊永續協作</title>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-zinc-950 text-white">
    <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl text-center">
        <p class="text-emerald-400 mb-4 tracking-[0.3em]">
          MIDLian Sustainable Partnership
        </p>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
          攜手永續<br />
          共創價值
        </h1>

        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          秘鍊永續協作致力於協助企業邁向淨零與永續發展，
          透過碳管理、ESG 與永續策略，
          為這片土地注入更多溫暖與善意。
        </p>

        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="#"
            class="bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-400 transition px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium"
          >
            了解服務
          </a>

          <a
            href="#"
            class="border border-zinc-700 hover:border-zinc-500 transition px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium"
          >
            永續揭秘
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>